          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-7 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-蕭樂善/Siau Lo̍k-siān]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12161.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12161.htm">著贏少年人 [ TIO̍H IÂN SIÀU-LIÂN-LÂNG ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">著贏少年人
 
濟濟&ecirc;少年人不止贊成基督教，也濟濟親像信者，也若毋是nih。Beh引chhōa這款<span style="font-family: " lang="EN-US&quot...<a href="artical-12161.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
