        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/49f52a6b982f2.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/49f52a6b982f2.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-7 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-楊世註/Iûⁿ Sè-chù]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12171.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12171.htm">迷信Ê故事 [ BÊ-SÌN Ê KÒ͘-SŪ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">迷信&Ecirc;故事
佇歸仁北&ecirc;地方，「吳樂、徐炭」。大家攏知是笑詼迷信。這个流傳已經真久，就是清朝<span style="font-f...<a href="artical-12171.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/49f52b0dd309c.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/49f52b0dd309c.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-7 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-盧樹河/Lô͘ Chhiū-hô]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12172.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12172.htm">時間 [ SÎ-KAN ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">時間
論時間&ecirc;價值，已經成做俗語，－「時間就是錢？」按呢講：是因為若用時間就會得著錢&ecirc;因端。總是毋若按呢。時間是智識。Koh<span style="color: #00000...<a href="artical-12172.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr>
          <td height="30" valign="middle" class="be12">
          	<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
          	  <tr>
          	    <td align="left" class="be12">第99頁，共108頁(共2,148筆資料)</td>
                <td align="right" class="be12"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td align='left'><a href='artical-dt3ap97.htm'><img src='../images/btn_pre.gif' width='50' height='20' border='0'></a></td><td align="left"><a href='artical-dt3ap0.htm'>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='gy13'>1</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>...</td><td class='gy13'><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='artical-dt3ap96.htm'><span class='gy13'>97</span></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='artical-dt3ap97.htm'><span class='gy13'>98</span></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td class='be13b'>&nbsp;&nbsp;99&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='artical-dt3ap99.htm'><span class='gy13'>100</span></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='artical-dt3ap100.htm'><span class='gy13'>101</span></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><td align="left">...<a href='artical-dt3ap107.htm'>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='gy13'>108</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></td><td align='right'><a href='artical-dt3ap99.htm'><img src='../images/btn_next.gif' width='50' height='20' border='0'></a></td><td class='be13b f14'>&nbsp;&nbsp;To Page &nbsp; </td><td><input id='inpPage' url='artical-dt3ap' max='108' class='style f14' type='text' value='99' size='2'></td><td>&nbsp;<a href="artical-d0t3a0p98.htm&amp;list=1#" id="chgPage">GO</a></td></tr></table></td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br><a href="artical-d0t3a0p98.htm&amp;list=1#"><img src="../images/btn_top.gif" width="50" height="20" border="0" style="float:right"></a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
